---
title: Classic Beef Rump & Twice-Cooked Potatoes with Mushroom Jus & Lemony Green Bean Salad
description: Does it get more classic than steak and potatoes? We don’t think so. This one is amped up with twice-cooked potatoes for an extra crispy crunch, and a hearty mushroom jus poured on as liberally as you please. There’ll be a line out the door for this meal.
This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.
